@startuml
!include ../../_common/style.puml

title Redis Provider 扩展组件关系图

left to right direction

package "Provider SPI" as spi {
  interface LockProvider
  class LockProviderCapability
}

package "Redis Provider\n(distributed-lock-provider-redis)" as redis_provider {

  class RedisLockProvider <<phase1>>
  class RedisLockKeyBuilder
  interface RedisLockScriptExecutor
  class RedisLockScripts

  class "acquire.lua" as acquire_lua <<Lua>>
  class "release.lua" as release_lua <<Lua>>
  class "renew.lua" as renew_lua <<Lua>>
  class "check.lua" as check_lua <<Lua>>

  class Redis <<External>>
}

LockProvider <|.. RedisLockProvider

RedisLockProvider --> LockProviderCapability : capability
RedisLockProvider --> RedisLockKeyBuilder : build keys
RedisLockProvider --> RedisLockScriptExecutor : execute scripts
RedisLockProvider --> RedisLockScripts : script paths

RedisLockScriptExecutor --> Redis : EVAL / EVALSHA

RedisLockScripts --> acquire_lua
RedisLockScripts --> release_lua
RedisLockScripts --> renew_lua
RedisLockScripts --> check_lua

note right of RedisLockKeyBuilder
  Redis Cluster 使用 hash tag：

  iron:lock:{namespace:lockName}:lock
  iron:lock:{namespace:lockName}:fence
end note

note right of RedisLockProvider
  一期能力：
  - ownerToken
  - Lua acquire
  - Lua release
  - Lua renew
  - Lua check

  fencing token 二期启用。
end note

@enduml
